</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-4C3F9EE8-F904-4226-B03C-6E9046737740" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-7542211F-BFCE-4E60-B9C4-67BD44AC391D" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-DB340B14-87E5-4FDB-8108-245D16C84FF1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
